								<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-gold-600/20 to-gold-500/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
									<Handshake class="w-6 h-6 text-gold-500" stroke-width="1.5" />
								</div>
								<div>
									<h3 class="text-gold-500 font-semibold mb-2">Forte Relação</h3>
									<p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Construímos parcerias duradouras baseadas em confiança e resultados.</p>
								</div>
